# modular-polynomial data (phi_files/).  A 28 MB subset is bundled via git add -f
# (see phi_files_manifest.txt): the classical Phi_l (l<=97) plus the class-invariant
# navigation and invariant->j polynomials the CM method uses over 128-384 bits.  The
# full ~2.2 GB database (all invariants/levels) is NOT redistributed -- see INSTALL.
phi_files/*
!phi_files/phi_j_*.txt

